  "prompt": "What is the average Outbrain's CTR for marketers?",
  "response": "As of the most recent data, Outbrain's Click-Through Rate (CTR) can vary depending on factors such as the industry, targeting strategy, and ad content quality. Generally, native advertising platforms like Outbrain often see CTRs ranging from 0.2% to 0.8%. However, there have been instances where marketers achieve higher CTRs, especially with optimized and engaging content.\n\nFor the most accurate and current information, it's best to refer to Outbrain's own metrics or case studies, or consult with industry reports and benchmarks relevant to your particular sector and audience.",
